      "content": "but it doesn't feel like love. it just feels like a hole. i look at the room where it happened and i just feel empty. like there's nothing left in me to even try anymore. i dont want to \"navigate\" anything. i just want to close my eyes and not have to deal with the weight of it. i just want it to be quiet. forever.",
